title: The Secret Life of 4 Year Olds UK
description:
The program follows a group of 4 year olds who are put together in a nursery for a day, having never met before. The same experiment is then conducted six months later to see how they have developed. Two overseeing scientists learned lots about language and social skill development from the experiment. Broadcast on Channel 4, Feb, 2015. 
Originally uploaded by MVGroup
